<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10665207>
    dc:description "Figure 2 Nectopsyche species.Nectopsyche aymore new species. A,forewing; B, head and thorax, dorsal; C,head and thorax, lateral.Nectopsyche splendida. D, forewing;E,head and thorax, dorsal; F, head and thorax, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10665207/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10665211>
    dc:description "Figure 4 Nectopsyche splendida (Navás, 1917). Male. A, inferior appendage, ventral; B, segment IX – X, lateral; C, segment IX, dorsal; D, phallic apparatus in full-erected state, lateral; E, phallic apparatus in relaxed state, lateral.Female. F, segment IX- X, dorsal; G, segment IX – X, vaginal apparatus, ventral; H, segment IX – X, vaginal apparatus, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10665211/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10665213>
    dc:description "Figure 5 Distribution maps.Highlighted in Southeastern Brazil.White triangle:Nectopsyche aymore new species; black triangle and black circle:Nectopsyche splendida (Navás, 1917). Black circle: central points, records without detailed location information." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10665213/files/figure.png" ;
